<p>The maximum credit for this element is 20 points.</p>

<p>
  MI4 credit is for providing information about how deep flood waters can be anticipated to be in
  given areas of the community. The depth of expected flooding gives the inquirer a better concept
  of the flood hazard than does the base flood elevation alone.
</p>

<section id="322d-1" aria-labelledby="322d-1-title">
